y abuse this for direct communication that bypasses network security restrictions \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eValue:\u003c/strong\u003e metadata.name={{mirrord-role}}.rules[0].resources includes the 'pods/portforward' resource \u003cbr\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eExcepted value:\u003c/strong\u003e metadata.name={{mirrord-role}}.rules[0].resources should not include the 'pods/portforward' resource"},"fullDescription":{"text":"Roles or ClusterRoles with RBAC permissions to port-forward into pods can open socket-level communication channels to containers. In case of compromise, attackers may abuse this for direct communication that bypasses network security restrictions Value: metadata.name={{mirrord-role}}.rules[0].resources includes the 'pods/portforward' resource Excepted value: metadata.name={{mirrord-role}}.rules[0].resources should not include the 'pods/portforward' resource"},"properties":{"security-severity":"4.0","name":"RBAC Roles with Port-Forwarding Permission","id":"RBAC Roles with Port-Forwarding Permission - 38fa11ef-dbcc-4da8-9680-7e1fd855b6fb [Taken from query_id] (kics)","description":"Roles or ClusterRoles with RBAC permissions to port-forward into pods can open socket-level communication channels to containers. In case of compromise, attackers may abuse this for direct communication that bypasses network security restrictions Value: metadata.name={{mirrord-role}}.rules[0].resources includes the 'pods/portforward' resource Excepted value: metadata.name={{mirrord-role}}.rules[0].resources should not include the 'pods/portforward' resource","tags":["security","checkmarx","kics"]}},{"id":"Role Binding To Default Service Account - 1e749bc9-fde8-471c-af0c-8254efd2dee5 [Taken from query_id] (kics)","name":"Role Binding To Default Service Account","helpUri":"https://checkmarx.com/resource/documents/en/34965-67042-checkmarx-one.html","help":{"text":"No role nor cluster role should bind to a default service account Value: subjects.kind=ServiceAccount.name is default Excepted value: subjects.kind=ServiceAccount.name should not be default","markdown":"No role nor cluster role should bind to a default service account \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eValue:\u003c/strong\u003e subjects.kind=ServiceAccount.name is default \u003cbr\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eExcepted value:\u003c/strong\u003e subjects.kind=ServiceAccount.name should not be default"},"fullDescription":{"text":"No role nor cluster role should bind to a default service account Value: subjects.kind=ServiceAccount.name is default Excepted value: subjects.kind=ServiceAccount.name should not be default"},"properties":{"security-severity":"4.0","name":"Role Binding To Default Service Account","id":"Role Binding To Default Service Account - 1e749bc9-fde8-471c-af0c-8254efd2dee5 [Taken from query_id] (kics)","description":"No role nor cluster role should bind to a default service account Value: subjects.kind=ServiceAccount.name is default Excepted value: subjects.kind=ServiceAccount.name should not be default","tags":["security","checkmarx","kics"]}},{"id":"Run Using Sudo - 8ada6e80-0ade-439e-b176-0b28f6bce35a [Taken from query_id] (kics)","name":"Run Using Sudo","helpUri":"https://checkmarx.com/resource/documents/en/34965-67042-checkmarx-one.html","help":{"text":"Avoid RUN with sudo command as it leads to unpredictable behavior Value: RUN instruction contains sudo Excepted value: RUN instruction shouldn't contain sudo","markdown":"Avoid RUN with sudo command as it leads to unpredictable behavior \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eValue:\u003c/strong\u003e RUN instruction contains sudo \u003cbr\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eExcepted value:\u003c/strong\u003e RUN instruction shouldn't contain sudo"},"fullDescription":{"text":"Avoid RUN with sudo command as it leads to unpredictable behavior Value: RUN instruction contains sudo Excepted value: RUN instruction shouldn't contain sudo"},"properties":{"security-severity":"4.0","name":"Run Using Sudo",