kmarx-one.html","help":{"text":"When pip is installing and extracting a maliciously crafted wheel archive, files may be extracted outside the installation directory. The path traversal is limited to prefixes of the installation directory; thus isn\u0026#39;t able to inject or overwrite executable files in typical situations. Affected versions are prior to 26.0.","markdown":"When pip is installing and extracting a maliciously crafted wheel archive, files may be extracted outside the installation directory. The path traversal is limited to prefixes of the installation directory; thus isn\u0026#39;t able to inject or overwrite executable files in typical situations. Affected versions are prior to 26.0."},"fullDescription":{"text":"When pip is installing and extracting a maliciously crafted wheel archive, files may be extracted outside the installation directory. The path traversal is limited to prefixes of the installation directory; thus isn\u0026#39;t able to inject or overwrite executable files in typical situations. Affected versions are prior to 26.0."},"properties":{"security-severity":"2.0","name":"Cve20261703","id":"CVE-2026-1703 (containers)","description":"When pip is installing and extracting a maliciously crafted wheel archive, files may be extracted outside the installation directory. The path traversal is limited to prefixes of the installation directory; thus isn\u0026#39;t able to inject or overwrite executable files in typical situations. Affected versions are prior to 26.0.","tags":["security","checkmarx","containers"]}},{"id":"CVE-2022-3219 (containers)","name":"Cve20223219","helpUri":"https://checkmarx.com/resource/documents/en/34965-67042-checkmarx-one.html","help":{"text":"GnuPG can be made to spin on a relatively small input by (for example) crafting a public key with thousands of signatures attached, compressed down to just a few KB.","markdown":"GnuPG can be made to spin on a relatively small input by (for example) crafting a public key with th